{"tid":1505264,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［預測］  明天狗隊記招對前線警務人員向天開槍既答覆","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T14:16:06.000Z","uid":11374,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1e7849304958fb40a45b5c14aad0deb48efd34","tid":1505264,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"正如我頭先所講啦 係啦~<br />\n我地既同事當時正面對極大既生命威脅 <br />\n係畫面所見 大批暴徙不斷向我地同事使用長棍 鐵棍 等攻擊性武器 嚴重威脅前線同事生命安全<br />\n係啦~ 我地既同事係別無他選既情況下<br />\n係啦~ 只好採取唯一既方法去驅散示威者<br />\n警方重申 我地一直都有使用武器既嚴格指引<br />\n係啦~ 係當時情況 我認為係合理既!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔撚洗理犬方講乜撚<br />\n牠點答唔撚重要<br />\n去到現階段 唔需要再吸納其他&quot;中立&quot;/藍絲無腦港豬<br />\n兩個月過去 所有人都已經有立埸<br />\n良知 有定冇! 就係咁簡單<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n重點係 推比國際睇<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3997a89588e039f2fc20faafc094b62dcdddaaf6","tid":1505264,"uid":275524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"文宣請入：快d spin 呢條片 如果唔係中間派遲早比統戰 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1505177/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1505177/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6fb9c83be935960e3a82267003f0eb2d85f151d8","tid":1505264,"uid":276527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:26:06.000Z","msg":"全世界一齊推9月1號塞機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1504779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1504779</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Dt098M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Dt098M.png&h=7129f0ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0db2c5829b6e44e2f1dc2f63ec3f348b080c254d","tid":1505264,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eb84SjE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEb84SjE.png&h=f313c8d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0f8d28cb9cf6